                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17140908-17-off88 t17140908-17-cd89"></join> last. Mr. Mitchell depos'd, That the late dreadful Fire in <placeName id="t17140908-17-crimeloc90">Houndsditch</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17140908-17-crimeloc90" type="placeName" value="Houndsditch"></interp>
